Question
========

A researcher has done research and comes up with the following table, where alpha = .05.

  -------- ---- ---- ---- --- Source df SS MS F Groups 4 40 Error 25 Total 29 90 -------- ---- ---- ---- ---

Can you reject the null hypothesis?

Answerlist
----------

* Yes
* No
* Undeterminable

Solution
========

Answerlist
----------

* Yes: Correct
* No: Incorrect
* Undeterminable: Incorrect
